{
  "id": "69e365f305d1a9f82e4d1bd5",
  "title": "おまえの開いているタブの数を言ってみろ……！",
  "created": 1776510455,
  "updated": 1776552462,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e365f305d1a9f82e4d1bd5",
      "text": "おまえの開いているタブの数を言ってみろ……！",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510455,
      "updated": 1776510455
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3663b0000000000871284",
      "text": "2026-04-18",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510524,
      "updated": 1776510534
    },
    {
      "id": "69e365f7000000000087127c",
      "text": " [nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510455,
      "updated": 1776510538
    },
    {
      "id": "69e365f8000000000087127e",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/5ffcdd96cda047ff932a35eea0f0d0ab]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510456,
      "updated": 1776510538
    },
    {
      "id": "69e365f7000000000087127d",
      "text": " \t`37 + 76 + 3 + 1 = 117`",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510456,
      "updated": 1776510538
    },
    {
      "id": "69e366240000000000871280",
      "text": " \tこれでも減った方",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510500,
      "updated": 1776510538
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3662a0000000000871281",
      "text": " \t\t前は 300件を超えてた",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510507,
      "updated": 1776510538
    },
    {
      "id": "69e36843000000000087128f",
      "text": " \t\tあとで読む代わりに使っているとこうなる",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776511043,
      "updated": 1776511077
    },
    {
      "id": "69e36d5a00000000004b223c",
      "text": " \t[Sidebery]",
      "userId": "607b0871492ba5001c53b4e6",
      "created": 1776512347,
      "updated": 1776512350
    },
    {
      "id": "69e367c6000000000087128e",
      "text": " \tなんとなくクオリアさんを召喚しておいた",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510918,
      "updated": 1776510927
    },
    {
      "id": "69e366c500000000006ecb5c",
      "text": " [Summer498.icon][{ 3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776510662,
      "updated": 1776510680
    },
    {
      "id": "69e366de00000000006ecb5e",
      "text": " \tこのページと d アニとアニメウィンドウ（ウィンドウはタブか？）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776510687,
      "updated": 1776510733
    },
    {
      "id": "69e366c500000000006ecb5d",
      "text": " [caki.icon][{ 66]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776510662,
      "updated": 1776510749
    },
    {
      "id": "69e36722000000000023b4b3",
      "text": "  スマホはあんまタブ閉じないので多い",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776510754,
      "updated": 1776510764
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3672d000000000023b4b4",
      "text": "  PCだと20を超えることはあんまないだろう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776510766,
      "updated": 1776510783
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3673f000000000023b4b5",
      "text": "   普段はだいたい10くらい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776510783,
      "updated": 1776510807
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3676a000000000023b4b6",
      "text": "  300くらいの猛者、井戸端にいそう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776510826,
      "updated": 1776510839
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3671100000000006ecb5f",
      "text": " [vlzs.icon][{ 0]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776510738,
      "updated": 1776514073
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3741800000000009aebba",
      "text": "  溜まるのが嫌でブラウザを閉じるときに破棄してる（設定の「開いていたタブを復元」をオフにしてる）",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514073,
      "updated": 1776514829
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3752900000000009aebc0",
      "text": "   PCをシャットダウンしてるので0",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514345,
      "updated": 1776514691
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3745d00000000009aebbc",
      "text": "  スマホはたぶん30タブぐらい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776514141,
      "updated": 1776515293
    },
    {
      "id": "69e378cc00000000009aebe3",
      "text": "   多いときは百個ぐらい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776515277,
      "updated": 1776515287
    },
    {
      "id": "69e378bb00000000009aebe0",
      "text": "  布団に持ち込む用のスマホのブラウザーでは小説サイトを3タブくらい開いてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776515260,
      "updated": 1776515271
    },
    {
      "id": "69e378bd00000000009aebe1",
      "text": "\t[sta.icon]1～10",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776515261,
      "updated": 1776550167
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e1a400000000003a1c18",
      "text": "\t\t調べ物してるときとか一時的に10くらいになることがある",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776542117,
      "updated": 1776550169
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e1ac00000000003a1c19",
      "text": "\t\t普段3以内をキープする",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776542125,
      "updated": 1776550169
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e1b500000000003a1c1a",
      "text": "\t\t「このタブなんだっけ」「どのタブに表示してたっけ」が一瞬でも生じるのが嫌だ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776542134,
      "updated": 1776550169
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4011f0000000000b2ffdf",
      "text": "\t\t似た話は[sta.icon]も前書いた気がする:",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776550176,
      "updated": 1776550198
    },
    {
      "id": "69e401280000000000b2ffe0",
      "text": "\t\t\t思い出せん",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776550185,
      "updated": 1776550187
    },
    {
      "id": "69e40614000000000016377c",
      "text": "\t\t\tどこかのページで開いているタブの数をアンケート的にとっていてそこで見たような気が[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1776551445,
      "updated": 1776551481
    },
    {
      "id": "69e409fc0000000000b2ffe1",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tまさにそう、私がページつくったはず[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776552445,
      "updated": 1776552462
    },
    {
      "id": "69e400df0000000000b2ffdb",
      "text": " [yosider.icon][{ 27]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776550111,
      "updated": 1776550174
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e5820000000000ad3fa5",
      "text": "  ↑PCで今開いているウィンドウのタブ数",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776543106,
      "updated": 1776543481
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e59a0000000000ad3fa6",
      "text": "   これは多いほうかも 10-20くらいで一旦OneTabにぶち込むことが多い",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776543130,
      "updated": 1776543179
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e6bb0000000000edcea9",
      "text": "    OneTabには5000くらいあった",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776543419,
      "updated": 1776543431
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e62d0000000000ad3faa",
      "text": "   [Chromeの垂直タブバー]を導入したので少し増えた",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776543277,
      "updated": 1776543311
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e65a0000000000ad3fab",
      "text": "   水平タブバーでタブをたくさん開いてfaviconしか見えずページを探すのに苦労する状態が嫌い",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776543323,
      "updated": 1776543381
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e5b90000000000ad3fa7",
      "text": "  スマホはあんまタブ閉じないので多い",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776543161,
      "updated": 1776543204
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3e5e50000000000ad3fa8",
      "text": "   先週スマホ替えたばかりなのでまだ100程度だが、これからも増え続けることだろう",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776543205,
      "updated": 1776543246
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3740a00000000009aebb9",
      "text": " [hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1776514058,
      "updated": 1776552021
    },
    {
      "id": "69e408550000000000406ed1",
      "text": " \tたまに200タブに到達する",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1776552022,
      "updated": 1776552040
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4086b0000000000406ed2",
      "text": "\t \t大体は調べ物でWebを徹底的に検索している場合に起こる",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1776552043,
      "updated": 1776552172
    },
    {
      "id": "69e408790000000000406ed3",
      "text": "\t \tGoogle,Google Scholar Duckduckgo, Braveでそれぞれ検索して関連ページも漁るとすごい数に",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1776552058,
      "updated": 1776552118
    },
    {
      "id": "69e408b60000000000406ed4",
      "text": "\t 普段は100+20ぐらい",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1776552118,
      "updated": 1776552128
    },
    {
      "id": "69e408530000000000406ed0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1776552019,
      "updated": 1776552019
    },
    {
      "id": "69e366550000000000871285",
      "text": "[タブ開き過ぎ] ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510549,
      "updated": 1776510845
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3677f000000000087128c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1776510847,
      "updated": 1776510860
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3677c000000000087128a",
      "text": "#クオリアさん #井戸端でしょうもないページを作る部",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776510845,
      "updated": 1776512048
    },
    {
      "id": "69e3759500000000009a89e8",
